### Health check
GET http://localhost:5000/api/health

### Login admin
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@minihobbies.lk",
  "password": "ChangeMe123!"
}

### List products
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products?search=hot%20wheels&minPrice=1000&maxPrice=10000

### Create category
POST http://localhost:5000/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Limited Editions",
  "description": "Rare hobby collector releases."
}

### Upload product images
POST http://localhost:5000/api/uploads/products
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

images=@sample-product.jpg
